pro2E.model

Class AntennaArray

  • java.lang.Object
    • pro2E.model.AntennaArray

  • public class AntennaArray
extends java.lang.Object
     The AntennaArray class represents an antenna array and contains a list with all the radiators and the diagram of said array.
    Author:
    pro2E - Team3
